<paragraph id="8B843E440C7CFFC2FF0450E1FF1B8348" blockId="5.[151,1437,1440,2005]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis id="B94FE2560C7CFFC2FF0450E1FECC8095" bold="true" box="[197,313,1476,1501]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41">Variation.</emphasis>
The height of the posterior carina of mesoscutellum is not constant, about 
<number id="3DF32C630C7CFFC2FB4C50E1FB178094" box="[1165,1250,1476,1500]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41" value="0.8500000000000001" valueMax="1.3" valueMin="0.4">0.4–1.3</number>
× diameter of an ocellus.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3216DCF0C7CFFC2FF045328FEDD8390" pageId="5" pageNumber="41" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8B843E440C7CFFC2FF045328FBB4836C" blockId="5.[151,1437,1440,2005]" box="[197,1089,1548,1573]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis id="B94FE2560C7CFFC2FF045328FEBE836D" bold="true" box="[197,331,1549,1573]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41">Etymology.</emphasis>
This new species is named after the generic name of the host plant.
</paragraph>
